;BIOMOLECULE: 1
THIS ENTRY CONTAINS THE CRYSTALLOGRAPHIC ASYMMETRIC UNIT
WHICH CONSISTS OF 2 CHAIN(S). SEE REMARK 350 FOR
INFORMATION ON GENERATING THE BIOLOGICAL MOLECULE(S).

ACCORDING TO AUTHORS, INTACT HUMAN CD23 IS THOUGHT
TO FORM A TRIMER, HOWEVER, THE EXACT RELATIONSHIP 
OF THE LECTIN DOMAINS IN THE MULTIMER IS NOT CURRENTLY 
KNOWN
;
